1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=This Time, Let Me Protect You=

4
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:50,510
Che,

5
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:51,840
let's go.

6
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:56,270
No.

7
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,670
Zhaoli belongs to me.

8
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,030
Yan Che, don't forget

9
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,040
that I've issued the decree.

10
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:06,040
She is no longer your wife.

11
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,870
Whether she's my wife or not

12
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,400
is up to Zhaoli.

13
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,480
(Ying Du,)

14
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,070
(you've always been protecting me.)

15
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,840
(This time,)

16
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:22,400
(let me do something for you.)

17
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:26,960
Ying Du,

18
00:01:27,350 --> 00:01:28,590
didn't you see?

19
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:31,040
If Che hadn't arrived in time just now,

20
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,975
Ye Li, who fancies you,

21
00:01:33,986 --> 00:01:35,040
would've skinned me alive,

22
00:01:35,224 --> 00:01:36,373
and my flesh would've rotted.

23
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:39,230
Every moment we've spent together

24
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,120
has been filled with pain.

25
00:01:43,230 --> 00:01:45,000
Let's not meet again.

26
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,760
Che,

27
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,320
let's go.

28
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,240
Zhaoli.

29
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,240
Zhaoli!

30
00:02:25,430 --> 00:02:26,800
Look, your clothes are all soaked.

31
00:02:26,978 --> 00:02:28,127
Go change into something dry.

32
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:35,430
I'm a little tired.

33
00:02:36,346 --> 00:02:37,480
I want to change my clothes.

34
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,400
I'll rest for a while.

35
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,190
Che, you scared me.

36
00:02:44,870 --> 00:02:45,710
Did he do this?

37
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:49,550
I...

38
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,360
Yan Che.

39
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,280
Yan Che, let me go!

40
00:03:00,386 --> 00:03:01,910
- Let me go!
- Whatever he did to you,

41
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:03,280
I'll do the same.

42
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,000
Why did you abandon me as well?

43
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:06,680
Calm yourself.

44
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:09,080
Whatever he has, I must have too.

45
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,710
Let go, Yan Che!

46
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:12,840
Have you lost your mind?

47
00:03:13,907 --> 00:03:15,817
Today, I'll teach you
a few self-defense moves.

48
00:03:15,887 --> 00:03:17,059
For times when I'm not around,

49
00:03:17,070 --> 00:03:18,450
they'll be enough to keep you safe.

50
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,120
How dare you wound me!

51
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:32,750
Zhaoli,

52
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:34,360
do you know how deeply

53
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,680
I've missed you during this time?

54
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,310
I can overlook

55
00:03:37,310 --> 00:03:39,190
whatever happened these days.

56
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,030
As long as your heart remains with me,

57
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:43,590
I can accept anything.

58
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,280
(Now,)

59
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:48,800
(only by killing him)

60
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,560
(can Ying Du survive.)

61
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:58,150
(I can't sway her with feelings.)

62
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,840
(I'll have to use Oracle's method.)

63
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,750
You're not Che at all.

64
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,190
You've killed

65
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,510
the real Che.

66
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:17,470
Mr. Yan,

67
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,720
the ruler has passed.

68
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:19,720
Mr. Yan!

69
00:04:30,980 --> 00:04:33,500
(Everlasting Joy)

70
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:35,910
Ying Du.

71
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,880
Ying Du.

72
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,560
Why?

73
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,240
Why did this happen?

74
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:49,120
Why has it come to this?

75
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,430
Why?

76
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,000
Ye Li,

77
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,270
wasn't his wound healed?

78
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,390
Why has Ying Du become like this?

79
00:04:58,630 --> 00:05:00,190
How dare you confront me?

80
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,190
If not for you,

81
00:05:02,420 --> 00:05:03,520
he'd never wear himself down

82
00:05:03,531 --> 00:05:05,270
again and again.

83
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:08,040
You're the one responsible
for his downfall.

84
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,670
No.

85
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:16,710
That's not true.

86
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:17,920
There must be a way.

87
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,950
There must be a way.

88
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,000
There must be.

89
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,960
Oracle.

90
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,800
Oracle, where are you?

91
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:32,180
(Oracle)

92
00:05:50,310 --> 00:05:51,150
Zhaoli,

93
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,310
you've finally come.

94
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,040
Oracle,

95
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:59,680
how can I save one
on the brink of death?

96
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:03,040
I knew this trial awaited you.

97
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,800
But if you wish to overcome it,

98
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,750
only one can survive this fate.

99
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:09,430
I urge you to think for yourself.

100
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,960
No.

101
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,310
I beg you; please save him.

102
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:16,750
No matter what it takes.

103
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,390
Oracle, I'm begging you.

104
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,160
Please, stand up first.

105
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,080
No.

106
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:22,750
I'm begging you.

107
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,390
Please, I need your help.

108
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,310
If you truly want to save him,

109
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,430
it must be life for life.

110
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,640
Zhaoli,

111
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:34,800
are you truly willing

112
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,310
to offer your heart's blood?

113
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,400
I am willing.

114
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,000
I am willing.

115
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,190
Thank you, Oracle.

116
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,430
I can't let you die like this.

117
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,160
I will trade my life

118
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,480
for yours.

119
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,480
Mr. Yan,

120
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,800
with her heart's blood,

121
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,800
not only will your wounds heal,

122
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:58,000
but your power will grow greatly.

123
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:02,390
Thanks to your brilliant plan,

124
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,430
I could so easily trap her

125
00:08:04,430 --> 00:08:06,070
in the Illusion Realm

126
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:08,330
and make her willingly offer
her heart's blood.

127
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,830
(Never thought she would go)

128
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:15,270
(to such lengths for Ying Du.)

129
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:18,480
But you must not let her know

130
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,360
she is inside the Illusion Realm,

131
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,800
or the realm will shatter.

132
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:25,240
Then the consciousness of you

133
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,040
could be trapped within.

134
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:28,270
It's fine.

135
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,750
Zhaoli is focused on saving her lover;

136
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,120
she can't think of anything else.

137
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,840
It's you I'm concerned with.

138
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:38,750
If I can command you,

139
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,510
others can just as easily use you too.

140
00:08:42,670 --> 00:08:44,550
Your usefulness ends here.

141
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:50,220
(Everlasting Joy)

142
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:54,920
Your Majesty,

143
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,920
you're awake.

144
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:59,440
If you go looking for her like this,

145
00:08:59,749 --> 00:09:00,963
something terrible will happen.

146
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,750
So, you already know everything.

147
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:06,590
Ye Li,

148
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,550
you know Yan Che stands against me.

149
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,790
Why do you keep joining forces with him?

150
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,130
I...

151
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,630
I was forced by him.

152
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:17,120
I had no choice.

153
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,270
What exactly is he planning?

154
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:23,960
He created an Illusory Realm,

155
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,960
making Wu Zhaoli believe

156
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,750
that you were already dead.

157
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,510
He then lured her

158
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,440
to offer her heart's blood

159
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,750
to mend his wounds
and restore his power.

160
00:09:36,512 --> 00:09:37,466
What did you just say?

161
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:45,440
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

162
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:52,240
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

163
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:56,980
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

164
00:09:56,980 --> 00:09:59,880
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

165
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:05,690
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

166
00:10:05,690 --> 00:10:09,390
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

167
00:10:09,740 --> 00:10:12,090
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

168
00:10:12,090 --> 00:10:16,130
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

169
00:10:16,130 --> 00:10:18,510
♪And that is enough♪

170
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:22,300
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

171
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:25,270
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

172
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:31,390
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

